aVBut really? Do you really have a place
p338
aVto stockpile 18 months worth of food? Twenty-four months worth of food?
p339
aVDo you want to view the pandemic threat
p340
aVthe way back in the 1950s
p341
aVpeople viewed the civil defense issue,
p342
aVand build your own little bomb shelter for pandemic flu?
p343
aVI don't think that's rational.
p344
aa(lp345
VI think it's about having to be prepared
p346
aVas communities, not as individuals \u2014
p347
aVbeing prepared as nation,
p348
aVbeing prepared as state, being prepared as town.
p349
aVAnd right now most of the preparedness
p350
aVis deeply flawed.
p351
aVAnd I hope I've convinced you of that,
p352
